squad.Brief.takeaways | hasValue | One additional candidate shape for the demo activity, in the same format as m1dgley's menu. Builder-shape: 'ship a new thing live, zero-to-one inside the window.' Adds the make-something-that-didn't-exist axis that A–E don't cover (A coordinates, B onboards, C queries, D deliberates, E repairs). Pairs naturally with E (repair → extend) or D (decide → make). Decision is still Rob's per law #5.
